    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear torque across the rev range. The drivetrain features a 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox paired with an M Variable Differential Lock for superior power delivery. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system serviced, and the rear subframe reinforced with plates to address common floor pan fatigue. Suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected of this platform. Showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, this M3 is mechanically sorted for the enthusiast who prioritizes performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 33500.0,
