    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really solid shape. It drives beautifully and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute. I've taken great care of it and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to chat!",
