    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically sorted, with the critical VANOS unit serviced and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain chassis rigidity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential that ensures predictable power delivery out of the apex. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and upgraded dampers, preserving the communicative hydraulic steering feedback these cars are known for. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain is robust and the cooling system has been overhauled for thermal efficiency. A visceral, analog performance machine ready for the next owner.",
